queries.query:
from(bucket: "AlpideData")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "X" or r["_field"] == "Y")  
  |> pivot(rowKey: ["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> keep(columns: ["X","Y"])

from(bucket: "AlpideData")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Horten")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "Y")
  |> group(columns: ["table"], mode:"by")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 30m, fn: count, createEmpty: false)

from(bucket: "AlpideData")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "X" )  
  |> group()
  |> count() 
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: int(v: r._value)  }))
